Running AIRS from source
=======================

On Fedora 18

sudo yum install wxPython gcc python-devel libxslt-python

Goto 'bin' folder:

tar zxvf storm-0.19.tar.gz
cd storm-0.19.tar.gz
sudo python setup.py install
cd ..

tar zxvf beautifulsoup4-4.1.3.tar.gz
cd beautifulsoup4-4.1.3
sudo python setup.py install
cd ..

tar xvjf Twisted-12.3.0.tar.bz2
cd Twisted-12.3.0
sudo python setup.py install
cd ..
